{
  "texts": [
    "One author conducted the task meticulously, while the other two authors rigorously reviewed the extracted data to ensure its accuracy and objectivity.",
    "Data synthesis aims to summarise and synthesise the extracted data pertaining to each RQ.",
    "The vote-counting method is utilised to aid in result interpretation, followed by a narrative synthesis to comprehensively report and discuss the outcomes for each question.",
    "Additionally, visual representations in the form of charts and tables are incorporated to enhance the clarity and presentation of the findings.",
    "Figure 1 displays the number of articles at each stage of the selection process."
  ]
}